OL,3,CWhy recession is now 'the base case'
OL,5,FHit number two is the uncertainty
OL,6,Faround which tariffs are negotiable
OL,7,Fand which are set in stone.
OL,9,FThe uncertainty makes it very
OL,10,Fdifficult for consumers and businesses
OL,11,Fto make big purchases and big
OL,12,Finvestment - because they can't know
OL,13,Fif the items will be a fifth cheaper
OL,14,Fagain in just a few weeks, or where in
OL,15,Fthe world demand will turn out to be
OL,16,Fmore resilient or less resilient.
OL,18,FSo something of a freeze on big
OL,19,Finvestments, big corporate deals and
OL,20,Fbig ticket consumer expenditure is
OL,21,Funder way.
